song.info:
───────────────────────────
Do not be fooled by the funky sample names! These are the same samples I've ripped and kept for half a year! :-)
After finals are over this week and I get home, I promise I will rip a new set of samples (double :-)) ───────────────────────────
- Lifestruck -
─═ by PhoenIx / kLf ═─ December 13, 1994
composed in ScreamTracker 3.2, it's the fourth time I've run ST.EXE! ───────────────────────────
Look at all this room for greets!
Leviathan: finish that 87! Hadji: Hadji!!!! (doesn't everyone say that?) :) Zer0: How about some REAL Indystrial Rage? Musicman: Keep Bass alive! Neurosis: You'll be recognizing some of these samples very soon :-) Stalker: Are the $5 checks pouring in yet? hehe Maelcum: Waiting for that KLF XMas surprise! Scoobs: I still think the audio CD is a good idea! Skaven: Pamela Anderson's #1 fan.. no gifs at ASM95! and.. necros uuDW rangeRick sophisto & the #trax gang! ───────────────────────────
·Andy Voss·vossa_rpi.edu· happy holidaze
